title: The Tick
description:
Far from complete, but a pretty good chunk of all The Tick comics that have ever been printed.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Issues 1-13 of 'The Tick V1' 
New England Comics, 1988-2000 (really just 1988-1993 - issue 13 was released seven years after issue 12), 
Written by Ben Edlund
Penciled by Ben Edlund, Maxfield Banks
Inked by Ben Edlund, Maxfield Banks, Dave Garcia, Jeff Whiting

'The Tick's Giant Circus of the Mighty'
New England Comics, 1992-1993, 29-32 pages
Written by Ben Edlund, Clay Griffith
Penciled and Inked by Ben Edlund, Dave Garcia, Alan Hopkins, Zander Cannon

'The Collected Paul The Samurai'
New England Comics, 1992, 99 pages
Written and Illustrated by Ben Edlund

Issues 1-10 of 'Man-Eating Cow'
New England Comics, 1992-1994, 24-36 pages
Written by Clay Griffith, Penciled by Alan Hopkins, Inked by Jeff Whiting, Alan Hopkins

Issues 1-9 of 'The Tick - Karma Tornado'
New England Comics, 1993-1995, 24-29 pages
Written by Ben Edlund, Chris McCulloch, Terry Collins, Clay Griffith, L.C. Cheverett
Penciled by Dave Garcia, Bill Neville, Chris McCulloch, Alan Hopkins, 
Inked by Dave Garcia, Ron Muns, Jeff Whiting,Rick Ketcham

'Chainsaw Vigilante' (Collects Chainsaw Vigilante 1-3 with a gallery)
New England Comics, 1996, 84 pages
Written and Illustrated by Zander Cannon

'The Tick - The Naked City' (Collects issues 1-6 of Chroma Tick, which are colored reprints of The Tick V1)
Marlow & Company, 1996, 177 pages
Written and Illustrated by Ben Edlund

'The Tick's Back'
New England Comics, 1997, 26 pages (cover says 40, though - not sure what is missing)
Written and Illustrated by Eli Stone
